title: Ranked TT? Where is it?? No notifications about disabling it? No discussions?
body: WHERE IS IT? IT WAS JUST HERE YESTERDAY.

replies.body: Ranked teams for 3v3 and 5v5 are currently on a ranked schedule for each region, and the time will defer depending on weekend and weekday.  The full schedule can be found at our [Ranked Team Schedule](https://support.riotgames.com/hc/en-us/articles/209964886-Ranked-Teams-Schedule) guide.  I hope that helps clear things up!

Thanks!! 

So.. I guess I misunderstood at first:

Basically, ranked teams can only be played at certain hours of certain days?

Is this due to some maintenance?

Or is League of Legends finally coming to an end?

It permanent and not because of maintenance
and only for ranked 5v5 teams and ranked TT (since there is only team ranked for 3v3)
